ZH: 我们正在申请一项专利来保护我们的发明。
EN: We are applying for a patent to protect our invention.

ZH: 他是一位专利律师，专门处理知识产权法律事务。
EN: He is a patent attorney who specializes in intellectual property law.

ZH: 这个发明已经获得了30项专利。
EN: This invention has obtained 30 patents.

ZH: 他们正在开发一种新药，并计划申请专利。
EN: They are developing a new drug and planning to apply for a patent.

ZH: 他的发明被授予了一项专利保护。
EN: His invention was granted patent protection.

ZH: 这个公司一年内申请了一百多项专利。
EN: This company applied for over a hundred patents within a year.

ZH: 他们的专利正在国际范围内得到保护。
EN: Their patent is protected internationally.

ZH: 他的创新想法被视为一个重要的专利。
EN: His innovative idea is regarded as an important patent.

ZH: 他们正在与专利局联系，准备递交申请。
EN: They are contacting the patent office to prepare their application.

ZH: 他们正在等待专利审批的结果。
EN: They are waiting for the result of the patent approval.

ZH: 这个专利将为他们带来巨大的商业利益。
EN: This patent will bring them significant commercial benefits.

ZH: 他的专利被引用为许多后续技术的基础。
EN: His patent is cited as the basis for many subsequent technologies.

ZH: 这个发明对生物技术领域是一个重要的专利。
EN: This invention is an important patent in the field of biotechnology.

ZH: 这家公司将专利权授予了一个合作伙伴，以推广他们的技术。
EN: This company granted the patent rights to a partner to promote their technology.

ZH: 他们正在考虑将这个专利出售给其他公司。
EN: They are considering selling this patent to another company.

ZH: 只有申请到专利，他们的发明才能得到保护。
EN: Their invention can only be protected if they obtain a patent.

ZH: 这个发明已经过专利审查并获得通过。
EN: This invention has undergone patent examination and has been approved.

ZH: 他们的专利正在通过国际合作获得保护。
EN: Their patent is being protected through international collaborations.

ZH: 专利技术的转让有时可以带来巨额收入。
EN: The transfer of patented technology can sometimes bring substantial income.

ZH: 这项专利保护了他们在市场上的竞争优势。
EN: This patent protects their competitive advantage in the market.
